blog.name: phandomreversebang
blog.title: Phandom Reverse Bang 2019
blog.description:
Welcome to the 4th edition of the Phandom Reverse Bang! We're a big bang in reverse; artists create themed pieces of art, and authors claim said work to write a fic based around them! 
  Mobile Navigation

title: 🚨Author Claiming is Open🚨
body:
The time is finally here for Authors to claim the art pieces and the beta that they want!

To claim your art, follow these instructions:

1: Go to this page and look through all of the art pieces

2: Find the piece that you want to claim and head on over to this spreadsheet! This spreadsheet is also linked on the page with the art so don’t worry about bouncing back and forth between this post and the art page!

3: Find the number that corresponds with your artwork. If it looks like this ↓ 

 congrats! That fic is open for claiming!

However, check to make sure that there isn’t a little tab in the corner ↓ 

The fics come on a first come, first serve basis!

Best suggestion if your fic is taken: don’t feel discouraged, go back onto the page and see if another picture speaks to you!

4: Comment your name and claim number onto the box corresponding with the correct number. Like so:

Once you click comment, the box will now appear with the little yellow tab in the corner as seen above. Once that is done, that’s it! You’re done!

If you’re claiming a beta, then you’ll go to the same spreadsheet as linked above, but instead, you’ll go to the bottom of the sheet and click the tab that says beta claiming

From there, you’ll do the exact same thing that you did for an art prompt, but this time for a beta! 

If anyone has any other questions: the admins will be available readily throughout the first wave with any answers they can offer! Happy claiming!

****As of right now, there is no successful way to claim on mobile so you will need to try and claim via a desktop or laptop computer****

summary: so i was thinking what *regular* people think of dan and phil when they stumble over the gaming channel? do they get the demon...
question: so i was thinking what *regular* people think of dan and phil when they stumble over the gaming channel? do they get the demon vibe? or do they  miss it? i never see these people in the comments and i wonder if you do
answer:
okay i can tell u this actually bc i made my friend who is Not a phan watch some gaming vids and her reactions were:

  • wow the black-haired guy really likes to win doesn’t he
  • they’re actually p funny
  • wow the black-haired guy really really likes to win
  • i like their accents
  • okay that guy (phil) just really hates losing

i don’t think she really had any demon thoughts aside from, whilst watching the cah vid, to ask if they were together (which is kinda demon but like there was no ‘oh my god they’re fucking’ or anything y’know)

i kinda want to do a study of non-phans who’ve never heard or dnp or seen the gaming channel but like watching gaming vids and like. have them watch a selection of vids just to see y’know??
